"title": "3212: Holy Spirit, and mission",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3212",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Holy Spirit directs and empowers believers in their missionary tasks, bearing witness to Jesus Christ and preparing the hearts of men and women to respond to him in faith.</p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit equips God's people</h2>\n<h3>He inspired the prophets</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30\">NEH 9:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job32:8\">JOB 32:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:16\">ISA 48:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:8\">MIC 3:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1\">HEB 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>He empowered Jesus Christ as Messiah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1\">ISA 42:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:16\">MAT 3:16</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:10\">MRK 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:21-Luke3:22\">LUK 3:21–3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:32-John1:34\">JHN 1:32–1:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a></p>\n<h3>He empowered the first Christians</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:16-Acts2:17\">ACT 2:16–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:17\">ACT 8:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:44\">ACT 10:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:15\">ACT 11:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:6\">ACT 19:6</a> <em>The outpouring of God's Spirit begins to extend beyond the Jews.</em></p>\n<h3>He empowers God's people today</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16\">JHN 14:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:26-Rom8:27\">ROM 8:26–8:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:3-1Cor12:7\">1CO 12:3–12:7</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit accomplishes the mission of God</h2>\n<h3>He convicts of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:8\">JHN 16:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:37\">ACT 2:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:24-1Cor14:25\">1CO 14:24–14:25</a></p>\n<h3>He directs mission</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2\">ACT 13:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:29\">ACT 8:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:19-Acts10:20\">ACT 10:19–10:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:4\">ACT 13:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:6-Acts16:10\">ACT 16:6–16:10</a></p>\n<h3>He inspires witnesses and speakers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:9-Acts6:10\">ACT 6:9–6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:19-Matt10:20\">MAT 10:19–10:20</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:11\">MRK 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:14-Luke21:15\">LUK 21:14–21:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:14\">ACT 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">ACT 4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:15\">ACT 11:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:9-Acts13:10\">ACT 13:9–13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5\">1TH 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:12\">1PE 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>He gives signs and wonders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:18-Rom15:19\">ROM 15:18–15:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:50\">JHN 1:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:13\">ACT 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:12\">2CO 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:5\">GAL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:4\">HEB 2:4</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's missionary activity is ongoing</h2>\n<h3>He cares for God's people involved in mission</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7\">JHN 16:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28\">ACT 15:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:7\">1PE 5:7</a></p>\n<h3>He sanctifies God's people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:10\">ROM 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:14\">ROM 8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:16\">ROM 15:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13\">2TH 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>He encourages God's people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:16\">ROM 8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:27\">ROM 8:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:17\">2TH 2:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:24\">1JN 3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:13\">1JN 4:13</a></p>",
